Kafka-springboot:
	-> kafka configuration can be provided directly in application.properties.
	-> define topic using @configuration annotation(here all configurations are defined inside config package.)
	-> run kafka and zookeeper before running the application 
	-> after running check followings
		-> http://localhost:8080/hi
		-> http://localhost:8080/kafka/publish?message=hello
			consumer application will print received msg on console itself. 

